Solaris 11.3 libc entry points differ in several cases.

In addition, 11.3 needs to define:
  * LOCK_* for the benefit of the synthetic crate::fs::fcntl_lock
  * a dummy value for SIGINFO, to avoid patching nix-0.29.0/src/sys/signal.rs
  * a value for O_DIRECT to avoid patching nix-0.29.0/src/fcntl.rs

